  'SNYK-JS-IMAGESIZE-17295814':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Build-time only — vulnerable path is docusaurus mdx-loader in @defra/interactive-map docs, never loaded by grants-ui runtime. No upstream fix available.'
        expires: '2026-07-02'
  'SNYK-JS-IMAGESIZE-17295816':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Build-time only — vulnerable path is docusaurus mdx-loader in @defra/interactive-map docs, never loaded by grants-ui runtime. No upstream fix available.'
        expires: '2026-07-02'
  'SNYK-JS-WEBPACKDEVSERVER-17353649':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Build-time only — webpack-dev-server via the docusaurus toolchain in @defra/interactive-map docs, never loaded by grants-ui runtime. Fixed in 5.2.5; interim ignore while the override is blocked by .npmrc min-release-age=7 (5.2.5 published 2026-06-12, installable from 2026-06-19). Replace with an overrides pin and remove this entry once it clears the cooldown.'
        expires: '2026-06-26'
  'SNYK-JS-JOI-17317897':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Transitive via @defra/fcp-audit-publisher (bundles joi@18.1.2); its schema uses no recursive Joi.link/self-reference, so the vulnerable code path is not reachable. Direct joi pinned to ^17 due to consumer constraint — awaiting fcp-audit-publisher release pinning joi >= 18.2.1.'
        expires: '2026-07-12'
  'SNYK-JS-JSYAML-17342520':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Fix version is incoming from Defra forms team - Inefficient Algorithmic Complexity [Medium Severity][https://security.snyk.io/vuln/SNYK-JS-JSYAML-17342520] in js-yaml@4.1.1'
        expires: '2026-07-16'
  'SNYK-JS-HTTPPROXYMIDDLEWARE-17375053':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Build-time only — http-proxy-middleware via webpack-dev-server in the docusaurus toolchain of @defra/interactive-map docs, never loaded by grants-ui runtime. Fixed only in 3.0.6/4.1.0, but webpack-dev-server@5.2.5 pins http-proxy-middleware ^2.0.9, so no in-range upgrade or override is viable. Remove once webpack-dev-server bumps to an http-proxy-middleware 3.x/4.x line.'
        expires: '2026-07-16'
  'SNYK-JS-SHELLQUOTE-17457810':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Build-time only — shell-quote via npm-run-all and webpack-dev-server/launch-editor in the dev toolchain, never loaded by grants-ui runtime. Fixed in 1.9.0; interim ignore while the override is blocked by .npmrc min-release-age=7 (1.9.0 published 2026-06-25, installable from 2026-07-02). Replace with an overrides pin and remove this entry once it clears the cooldown.'
        expires: '2026-07-09'
  'SNYK-JS-FASTURI-17675102':
    - '*':
        reason: 'Low risk — transitive via ajv@8.20.0 (fast-uri ^3.0.1), used only for JSON-Schema $id/$ref URI resolution, not for host allowlisting or redirect checks, so the interpretation-conflict path is not reachable at runtime. Fixed in 3.1.3, but both 3.1.3 and 4.0.1 were published 2026-06-29 and are blocked by .npmrc min-release-age=7 (installable from ~2026-07-06). Replace with an overrides pin to fast-uri@3.1.3 and remove this entry once it clears the cooldown.'
        expires: '2026-07-09'
  'SNYK-JS-BRACEEXPANSION-17706650':
